                  PM of India recommended somebody just to find a befitting
                  response of rejection from Shri. KK Birla, the then Chancellor.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
            <br>
            <article class="blog_item">
              <div class="blog_item_img">

                <a href="#" class="blog_item_date">
                  <h3>Many Firsts</h3>
                </a>
              </div>

