              </div>

              <div class="blog_details">
                <p>No attendance policy. You can attend the classes if you wish and it
                  is on a voluntary basis. Absolute freedom is given and that's what
                  makes the students excel in their passion.</p>
                <p>The institute is also known for the flexibility that it offers to
                  students. Apart from opting for dual degree programs, students can
                  also opt for transferring courses from one program to another.</p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="blog_item">
