                  <h3>Strongest Alumni</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="blog_details">
                <p>One of the strongest and well maintained alumni networks,
                  BITSAA, recognised worldwide.</p>
                <p>
                  Since the formation of BITS Students Alumni Association, alumni
                  students participating in the development of the institute has
                  increased. Meetings among past students and the current students
                  are repeatedly arranged, where students from the institution like
                  founders of Hotmail, Wipro or Bharat Forge interact on a regular
