                  <h3>BITS Connect 2.0.</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="blog_details">
                <p>All the four campuses of BITS are inter-connected through a
                  project called BITS Connect 2.0 . For instance, through this initiative,
                  a student from Goa Campus can not only attend lectures, guest
                  talks by eminent people at PILANI, HYDERABAD, or DUBAI
                  campuses, he/she can also interact with them online, pose
                  questions and get them clarified immediately. Thus, path leaders by
                  introducing remote education and opened a way for collaborative
                  research and development among the sister campuses</p>
              </div>
            </article>

