                  <h3>Moment of Proud</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="blog_details">
                <p>Furthermore, BITS Pilani has recently been declared as one of the
                  six Institutes of Eminence by the Government of India. Apart from
                  contribution to research, quality of faculty and the peer-viewed
                  journals released by the participating institutes were some of the
                  factors considered for selection purposes.</p>
                <p>
                  While public institutes selected under this scheme would be
                  receiving funding, private institutes like BITS Pilani would be getting
                  complete autonomy from regulations.
                </p>
              </div>
            </article>

